            <p class="justified">
                In commemoration of this newly-made, hip and happenin' author's website, FREE downloads of Patrick's brand new and very first short story collection, Gravedigger: Six Feet Deep, are now available through this site.
            </p>
            <p class="justified">
                This self-released collection of six supernatural-western stories follow the exploits of the title figure, who made his first literary appearance in "The Stranger," originally published in Sanitarium Magazine #37 and included here for your reading pleasure -- along with five previously unpublished stories. Download the collection and follow the gunslinging Gravedigger as he traverses a weird and wild west fraught with horror and danger!
            </p>
            <p class="justified">
                Downloadable files of the collection have been included for ePub (NOOK), Mobi (Kindle), and PDF files for your various reading conveniences, or you can just read the collection on the site itself.
            </p>
            <p class="justified">
                Please download, read, spread the word, and of course, enjoy the collection!
            </p>

